<span id="freeTextContainer6935661148197065155">Winner of the 1948 Pulitzer Prize for Fiction<br/>Enter the exotic world of the South Pacific, meet the men and women caught up in the drama of a big war. The young Marine who falls madly in love with a beautiful Tonkinese girl. Nurse Nellie and her French planter, Emile De Becque. The soldiers, sailors, and nurses playing at war and waiting for love in a tropic paradise.</span>

