<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/726749-i-am-curious-about-michener-s-research-for">I am curious about Michener&#39;s research for this book. What aspects are history and which are his invention? He used actual historical figures in his later writing, but are any of these characters based on real persons?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
