<div class='communityAnswer'>
<div class='communityAnswerBody'>
<div class='answererUserIcon'>
<a class="leftAlignedImage userPhoto" href="/user/show/5141125-zorro"><img alt="" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/users/1370021729i/5141125._UY100_CR16,0,100,100_.jpg" /></a>
</div>
<div class='communityAnswerTextContainer'>
<span class='communityAnswererName'>
<a href="/user/show/5141125-zorro">Zorro</a>
</span>
<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">I think he lived the story while stationed in the South Pacific during WWII. Of course he embellished the actual events and used his imagination and i<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">I think he lived the story while stationed in the South Pacific during WWII. Of course he embellished the actual events and used his imagination and invented characters as well. <a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
</div>
