<span id="freeTextContainer7078718956355823413">Tales Of The South Pacific won the Pulitzer Prize in 1948. Another WWII novel, but this one is a series of short stories of the war in the pacific. James Michener is a great story teller and I enjoyed his writing. I give Tales Of The South Pacific 4 stars.</span>

