          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/51183187-darren?shelf=guardian-1000">guardian-1000</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/51183187-darren?shelf=author-first">author-first</a>, 
