        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1719595307" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer16216254285322509643">If you want to know what life was like in the US military in the Pacific in WW2 then this is the book for you! Some action sequences, but mostly concerned with the waiting around/R&amp;R/behind-the lines/support roles etc. Rather non-fic/memoir-y, but very nicely written up by Michener, with interesting characters and, although episodic, kept looping back to earlier stories so sufficiently satisfying as a novel.<br/></span>

          </span>
        </div>


